tourBios.curYrHigh: A final-round 67 at Florida's Qualifying Tournament resulted in a solo third-place finish...Was T58 at the PC Financial Open, PGA TOUR Canada's first tournament...Thanks to three rounds in the 60s at the Bayview Place Island Savings Open, was T38.
tourBios.personal: Favorite movies are "Braveheart" and "The Wolf of Wall Street."...Favorite athletes to watch are Tiger Woods, Lionel Messi, Cristiano Ronaldo and Zlatan Ibrahimovic...Dream foursome would include Arnold Palmer, Jack Nicklaus and Ben Hogan...Worked as a postman and bartender following college...Twitter name is @paulhcormack.

dyn.dynBios: 1st Team All-American at McLennan Community College
dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T38th in 2014 at the Bayview Place Island Savings Open presented by Times Colonist.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 85th in Par Breakers on the PGA TOUR Canada.
